{"tid":1586064,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【行動】急需事後文宣！！！「為中國而戰」既爆頭阿叔肯定會被大造文章","createTime":"2019-09-21T19:10:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T05:48:52.000Z","uid":25178,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"e72f71f0d76f306324fa36e2bd82c3741e025953","tid":1586064,"uid":25178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T19:10:21.000Z","msg":"藍絲page已用<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「我為中國人而戰」</span></span>做文宣<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Dont.Politics/videos/2222085501237148/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FDont.Politics%2Fvideos%2F2222085501237148%2F&d=oV4CUVDy1gIsxIQuXHWa%2FYtKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=a5947082\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Dont.Politics/videos/2222085501237148/</a><br />\n中共要人反對香港，無非都係一招<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「 煽動民族主義」</span></span> <br />\n咁班愛國撚就會上晒身<br />\n一開始扣港獨帽子如是<br />\n「我支持警察你們可以打我」如是<br />\n今次「我為中國人而戰」亦會如是<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一定要搶文宣陣地<br />\n釐清事情來龍去脈</span></span><br />\n<br />\n【前傳】白衫大叔挑釁並企圖用玻璃樽襲擊市民，市民之後才自衛還擊。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkindigenous/videos/753158045107916/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkindigenous%2Fvideos%2F753158045107916%2F&d=oV4CUVDy1gIsxIQuXHWa%2FYtKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=678938df\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkindigenous/videos/753158045107916/</a><br />\n仲有一條另外角度<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/fans.hkgolden/videos/447629739180909/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffans.hkgolden%2Fvideos%2F447629739180909%2F&d=oV4CUVDy1gIsxIQuXHWa%2FYtKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=1dca3163\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/fans.hkgolden/videos/447629739180909/</a><br />\n<br />\n其他事件既源頭<br />\n【以正視聽】女手足、女記者被襲擊 勇武前線手足以武制暴 鄉黑勢力敗走元朗<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1585986\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1585986</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n-有大批親中黑社會，在元朗空群而出，向女性示威者，或女記者、女救護埋手非禮，甚至襲擊她們。其間，有示威者上前，以武力將他們制服。遇襲反擊的女示威者大叫：「咪以為我哋好蝦呀！」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/2787894407949833/posts/2991280674277871?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F2787894407949833%2Fposts%2F2991280674277871%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=oV4CUVDy1gIsxIQuXHWa%2FYtKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=42fc5f48\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/2787894407949833/posts/2991280674277871?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勞煩大家幫守喺唔同地方釐清</span></span>"},{"pid":"630de161dd10760164cfb627baec6d922518f656","tid":1586064,"uid":143319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T19:11:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9851a281e6f98a62254eeecd4d1152d752ea293c","tid":1586064,"uid":143319,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T19:11:14.000Z","msg":"請大家一齊正名<br />\n❌私了<br />\n✅為民除害<br />\n✅以武制暴<br />\n✅自衛反擊"},{"pid":"09fe1753f0251f4b2a569d087fe3c44ed1e1c3a5","tid":1586064,"uid":143319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T19:11:24.000Z","msg":"612 721 811 831901 新屋嶺 黨鐵<br />\n<br />\n922 1200 沙田巡迴合唱團 和你shop<br />\n922 1200 機場交通壓力測試<br />\n<br />\n927 2000 聲援及關注新屋嶺被捕者人權集會<br />\n<br />\n929 全球反共運動<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"47cc63e3576d175285c573f9b25d38423672f0a2","tid":1586064,"uid":85574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T19:11:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"25f92746f45d2aebe32216f582245f8fbf7a72e6","tid":1586064,"uid":36420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T19:11:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"05088c770eb76fefb6a62c4ea00493822ed16698","tid":1586064,"uid":143319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime